refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
EnchantDictionaryfalseenchant_broker_request_dict EnchantBrokerbroker stringtag
create a new dictionary using tag, the non-empty language tag you wish to request a dictionary for ("en_US", "de_DE", ...)

&reftitle.parameters;



  &enchant.param.broker;

   tag



     A tag describing the locale, for example en_US, de_DE

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;



   &enchant.changelog.broker-param;


    8.0.0

     On success, this function returns an EnchantDictionary instance now;
     previoulsy, a &resource; was retured.

  &reftitle.examples;



    A enchant_broker_request_dict example


     Check if a dictionary exists using
     enchant_broker_dict_exists and request it.



<?php
$tag = 'en_US';
$broker = enchant_broker_init();
if (enchant_broker_dict_exists($broker,$tag)) {
    $dict = enchant_broker_request_dict($r, $tag);
}
?>
